headline: Lennar Now Selling at New Port Corners, Bringing Family-Friendly and 55+ Lifestyle Living to New Port Richey, FL.
summary: Lennar, one of the nation's leading homebuilders, is now selling at New Port Corners, a vibrant master-planned community of single and multi-family homes in New Port Richey, FL. Featuring 22 thoughtfully crafted floorplans available across two communities, New Port Corners offers ample options for all ages, in addition to a 55+ Active Adult Lifestyle community, with modern home designs and resort-style amenities that cater to a wide range of lifestyles.
